name: Franz Roh - Digital finger painting
description:
My first NFT job.

A non-casual portrait of Franz Roh. Precisely the creator of the term "magical realism" has more than deserved to become my first NFT work.

"..." Humanity seems unfailingly destined to continually oscillate between devotion to the world of reality and an imagined world, and indeed, if this breathing rhythm of history ever stops, there seems to be nothing left but the death of the spirit ". .."

Franz Roh was a German historian, photographer, and art critic.
